          "length": {
            "number": 10,
            "unit": "minutes"
          }
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "step": "Roll the dough out on a well-floured surface, large enough to cut out 3, 7-inch circles out of each half (save the scraps). Line each cup of a large-sized muffin tin with the dough. (It won't look very pretty, you just kind of have your way with it to get it pressed in there.) Refrigerate the filled tins as well as the dough scraps 15 minutes to firm back up.",
          "ingredients": [
